m be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten direct per Po<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t an Frau Hofräthin <rs ref="#pmb36421" type="person">von Pollanetz</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb40392" type="place">Wien I. Domga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e 6</rs>.</p></postscript></div></body></text></TEI>